54a4684fcb79a1e27740d3c67e61ceaf069aed05399ea662b3dbd5a8ef9a69fbaa2aa0e1fc01c122b0471cc11d437cf0c2c52ec50ee9848457f6ab4e0e364b43  0001-refactor-remove-mlite-dependency.patch
"
